{"type": "article", "id": 42726, "title": "川久保玲的 DSM 要开到洛杉矶，以及，巴黎世家铅笔 5 欧一根| 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-07-06T03:19:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 905, "name": "Dover Street Market"}, {"id": 1580, "name": "巴黎时装周"}, {"id": 3203, "name": "Balenciaga"}, {"id": 3340, "name": "Valentino"}, {"id": 3865, "name": "adidas Originals"}, {"id": 9472, "name": "Colette"}, {"id": 12763, "name": "Maison Margiela"}, {"id": 34574, "name": "咖喱"}, {"id": 42102, "name": "高达"}, {"id": 42103, "name": "汤勺"}, {"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170706110304FREBD9TfOCSKW7az.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-07-05/christopher-bailey-s-out-as-burberry-ceo-he-couldn-t-be-happier\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Marco Gobbetti 正式出任 Burberry CEO</strong></a> | Marc Gobbetti 担任了六个月的亚洲临时执行主席，昨日起正式接任 Burberry 的 CEO 一职。目前，他已组建全新创意团队，拉来了 Dior 原女士皮具首席设计师 Sabrina Bonesi 和销售总监 Judy Collinson。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/retail-store-closures-2017-macys-bcbg-american-apparel-wet-seal-abercrombie-limted-jc-penney-sears-10842214/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>今年美国零售业关店数或将增至 9452 家</strong></a> | 面对电子商务带来的更激励竞争，美国关店潮还将继续。Fung Global Retail &amp; Technology 追踪全球零售业并指出，2017 年关闭的零售门店数量已经远远超过 2008 年金融危机时期。预计到今年年底，美国关店数量将达到 9452 家，比 2008 年还要多 53%。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/true-religion-apparel-files-ch-11-bankruptcy-court-protection-10939190/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>美国高端牛仔品牌 True Religion 递交了破产申请</strong></a> | 周三，True Religion Apparel Inc. 递交了破产保护申请。资料显示，该品牌的负债在 1 亿至 5 亿美元之间，在前 30 名无担保债权人中，提出索赔的大部分是供应商或物业业主。 True Religion 在 2013 年 5 月被 TowerBrook Capital Partners 以 8.35 亿美元的价格收购，后者旗下的投资还包括 Jimmy Choo，但它已经决定为 Jimmy Choo 寻求买家，完全退出时尚和奢侈品业务。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>川久保玲的<a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/business-features/dover-street-market-comme-des-garcons-open-in-los-angeles-10938181/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Dover Street Market 打算在洛杉矶开店</a>。这家店位于一个停车场内的巨大仓库里，占地约一万平方英尺，计划在 2018 年 3 月开幕。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105347SXrYjH6nhlaL1xtv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.749754\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105347s6wxjt1JMHnVBOgz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105347whe5voESXcJpTyYV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750564\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>卖咖喱的日本餐厅 CoCo 壱番屋和高达合作，特制了<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/ichibanya-coco-curry-house-mobile-suit-gundam\" rel=\"nofollow\">「HGUC 1/144 RX-78-2 GUNDAM CocoICHI Extra Finish Ver.」</a>高达汤勺，只要在 7 月 14 日至 8 月 31 日期间在日本地区的 CoCo 壱番屋内消费满 900 日元以上，即可参加抽奖获取高达汤勺。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105333yHh9vtjNA0mU6Oz4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105333gt9dzPCYNxXE5sJG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/jam-home-made-2017-commodity-series\" rel=\"nofollow\">增井元纪主理的日本手工配饰潮牌 JAM HOME MADE，推出了“日用品”主题挂饰，</a>包括衣夹、润唇膏等，还挺有趣的。 </p><p>该系列将于 7 月 8 日在 JAM HOME MADE 网店及门店发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707061053125nS6aF1VMELKgIZA.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105305Y01XPl8Nkt6OWhmf.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105317hjHLIdoTuYeqi7Em.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707061053055kWmSjEuYoa8wU9h.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105305wFAvPZGJtLHVOE2d.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/balenciaga-collete-pencils\" rel=\"nofollow\">Balenciaga 要在 colette 卖铅笔了</a>，比起天价购物袋，这系列一式四款的铅笔每支售价 5 欧元，可以在 <a href=\"http://en.colette.fr/catalog/product/view/id/564180/s/crayon-internet-rouge-blanc/category/12934/\" rel=\"nofollow\">colette 官网</a>购买。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105226v7S80Afo4cnZ3mqa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/adidas-originals-nmd-2017-fall-winter-accessories\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas Originals 发布了 2017 秋冬系列系列</a>。包括灵感来自 Copenhagen 的服装系列，还特别融入了人气 NMD 鞋款上的「The Brand with 3 Stripes」设计和日式美学。NMD 配饰系列有背包、手袋、电脑包、行李箱、腰包、钥匙扣等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105147Stn5oeRrYlBQi3qf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105145nfD7Wy4gaEOmS5do.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105147zjJyimeb1VSKWtaF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105147Xi5ygnARxvtr79z6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105146LlTOPZHNXeU0d2kj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105145p8C0rxlHa2JoRzkY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105145oQKu86UAFti0RvLp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105146kVXpLx5MqaPrGlhu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105146bUZSCNgRG5THW1zp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105209yOnhjrNo8CWBb75M.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105209b68g5dnpD0AOeiMI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707061052092C3j8rAhulDp4MIi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105210ASwbCy5gFouzXUT3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105210BIp4iVYctrab79ZA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105210B3mdWEOfG2RQxXIF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105210ej8nJqk1cboOZYR4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105211Cj6ioMGNhl52Q38m.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707061052114wYjTRkXvlFEAq3s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105211YEDyvnl9KaLPN7xJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105211WXoBZr6AP4CtvE1I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105211aMYpFj3mce7BUOwJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105212pZuUFW7ByYV3z4qb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>巴黎时装周上，各大品牌纷纷发布了自己的 2017 秋冬系列。 </p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/fall-couture-2017/paris/maison-martin-margiela/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maison Margiela </a>试图用网纱、拼贴、不规则剪裁、柔和的色调阐述一种带有浪漫艺术气息的“新魅力”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105125v7TIx3NEmwYyPGdl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502930\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105121epSVMg3E62f81tBT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105121O7YkyCJog08TwnLb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105120QMTph2jG7USWg1Fe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105122Z7hbTJ6e5EzutgN3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105122DOLEgxRY4peMWJnA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105123mZtMOdQShve4NE6l.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105123hjSu9Be6H2MXynOR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105124U1tx0D5B7RoKqIQs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/fall-couture-2017/paris/valentino/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valentino</a> 带来的女装高级定制系列，用色大胆、风格鲜明，热烈又不失优雅。</p><p>设计师 Pierpaolo Piccioli 称它是“关于神圣的反思”。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105025DM2wVlqfCnoiBdh1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105025TWP7omfA6vqDwVEB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105039XnrdlbAfeQ7JsIhz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105038gWQOALJ1VmCKoStF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105040A0fmTMdb6GxF5chw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105042hLpXNV3TczADWd8H.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105042wjcyW61HuPr5z2KE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105043is7TOVjHc3meUCqN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105044ZzYaiJvXtDTFE1Iy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105044joG2lIq1vHL5XA9E.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105045XausPJM2qUAWBjyd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105046CxpO1KVH8T095IlX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707061050463BHLGfxmURion17I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105046A87nzb9fdW1ZqkyE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105048OQqeS1DYnGrVdkKo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105048vjHNFmxMZbo38zqi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707061050502UuJeoE5b7jyCIs4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.469985\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105050PSCDu4gkAdfWoRyX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105050v32fB4nAqkSjIWd5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105051GYfEDvboqN4kpm1h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105051ZafoPVFJtKNlIQh0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707061050526bLnlH1c5UOJYXgV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170706105052BUaedYASk4EC2XN8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/fall-couture-2017/paris/valentino/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">wwd</a>、<a href=\"http://hobby.dengeki.com/news/405337/\" rel=\"nofollow\">hobbydenki</a></p>"}